last_episode_to_air.name: Picture Perfect
last_episode_to_air.overview: Dr. Ross and Dr. Ryan team up to investigate a dog's inability to walk. Dr. Tony helps a rescue dog with a bad hip get ready for a new home. And, Dr. Ross meets up with a parrot who is old enough to be a Henderson brother.

name: Hanging with the Hendersons
overview: Meet the Hendersons, Tony, Ross and Ryan, veterinary doctors who run Colorado's Fox Hollow Animal Hospital. Dr. Ross is best known as the vet who calmed a nervous dog with his serenading and guitar playing.

episodes.name: Meet the Pack
episodes.overview: Colorado's Fox Hollow Animal Hospital is run by an endearing family of vets.

episodes.name: Meet the Parents
episodes.overview: Dr. Ross has his hands full when a sick dog is rushed to the clinic after eating a bag of pot.

episodes.name: Born to be Wild
episodes.overview: It's double the trouble when Dr. Ryan and Dr. Tony tag team on a rare double knee surgery.

episodes.name: Donkey Dentist
episodes.overview: Dr. Ross travels to a donkey rescue to get a refresher on equine care.

episodes.name: Music is Medicine
episodes.overview: It's a parade of hula hoops and puppies when Dr. Tony and Dr. Ross visit a puppy rescue in need.

episodes.name: Snake, Rattle and Roll
episodes.overview: The Fox Hollow crew band together to help clinic dog Barrington lose weight.

episodes.name: Call of the Wild
episodes.overview: When a young dog gets bitten by a snake, Dr. Tim comes to the rescue. Dr. Ryan helps a Great Dane that has chewed through his own tail. Dr. Ross performs mouth surgery on a collie with a potentially cancerous mass.

episodes.name: It Takes a Village
episodes.overview: When an injured wolf-hybrid arrives at the clinic, the team comes together to help. While Dr. Ross heads out to a grade school classroom to share his love of veterinary medicine, Dr. Ryan and Dr. Tony head to a free veterinary clinic to lend a hand.

episodes.name: From Kittens to Kangaroos
episodes.overview: Dr. Tony is asked to handle a rare procedure in a young borzoi hound. Dr. Ryan deals with a bizarre dental discovery. Dr. Ross has his hands full with an albino kangaroo.

episodes.name: Hits and Misses
episodes.overview: Dr. Ross spays and neuters adorable kittens. Dr. Tony works on his vet tech's beloved dog.

episodes.name: All Creatures Great And Small
episodes.overview: From the biggest dog the clinic has ever handled, to the smallest toe on a tiny cat's foot, the vets of Fox Hollow have to be ready for every eventuality.
